Mix cornstarch, broth, water, soy, sugar, garlic and ginger in saucepan. Cook and stir until mixture boils and thickens. Thread alternately beef, mushrooms and onions on 4 long skewers. Grill kabobs 20 min. or until done, turning and brushing often with broth mixture. Place 1 tomato on end of each skewer. Heat remaining broth mixture to a boil. Serve with kabobs and rice.